snippet.title: Amazon Sponsored Brands Advertising Explained
snippet.description:
In this video, I explain what Amazon Sponsored Brands Ads are and how to use them. 

Sponsored Brands are creative ads that can help customers discover your brand ahead of peak seasonal and deal events, like Amazon Prime Day. 

To learn more about how to get started with Sponsored Brands, click here: https://advertising.amazon.com/solutions/products/sponsored-brands?ref_=a20m_us_hnav_smb_p_sb?ref_=org_infl_yt_na_us_Mina_vid_Spring1__2024
